Achievements.Name: Rookie Angler
Achievements.Description: Enter a Tournament mode event.

Achievements.Name: First Catch
Achievements.Description: Catch 1 fish of any species.

Achievements.Name: Something's Fishy
Achievements.Description: Find and cast into a fishing spot on any lake.

Achievements.Name: Lightning Catch
Achievements.Description: Be the first competitor to catch a fish in a Tournament mode event.

Achievements.Name: First Steps
Achievements.Description: Finish a Tournament mode event.

Achievements.Name: Perfect Form
Achievements.Description: Perform a perfect cast.

Achievements.Name: Perfect Hook
Achievements.Description: Get a fish on your line with a perfect hook.

Achievements.Name: Flying Fish
Achievements.Description: Catch a fish of any species by flipping it into your boat.

Achievements.Name: Confident?
Achievements.Description: Weigh in early during a Tournament mode event.

Achievements.Name: Challenger
Achievements.Description: Complete any Challenge in Free Fishing mode.

Achievements.Name: The One That Got Away
Achievements.Description: Lose a fish.

Achievements.Name: Isn't She Cute!
Achievements.Description: Raise a lure's attractiveness to its maximum level during a retrieve.

Achievements.Name: Original Feeling
Achievements.Description: Catch a fish with the Rapala® Original Floater® lure.

Achievements.Name: So Close, Yet So Far
Achievements.Description: Finish a Tournament mode event in 2nd or 3rd place.

Achievements.Name: Is That Who I Think It is?
Achievements.Description: In Tournament Mode, begin fishing alongside each competitor on the lake while they are fishing.

Achievements.Name: Multitasking
Achievements.Description: Finish a Secondary Objective in a Tournament mode event.

Achievements.Name: The Big One
Achievements.Description: Catch a record fish of any species.

Achievements.Name: The 10th Grade
Achievements.Description: Catch a total of 10 fish.

Achievements.Name: Victory!
Achievements.Description: Finish in 1st place in any event in Tournament mode.

Achievements.Name: Journeyman
Achievements.Description: Drive your boat for more than 5 minutes during a Tournament mode event and finish in the top 5.

Achievements.Name: Intermediate Angler
Achievements.Description: Complete a tier in the Rookie Season of Tournament mode.

Achievements.Name: Driven
Achievements.Description: Complete all events in the first tier of any season in Tournament mode.

Achievements.Name: Advanced Angler
Achievements.Description: Complete the Rookie Season in Tournament mode.

Achievements.Name: Friendly Angler
Achievements.Description: Finish the Rookie Season in Tournament mode with less than 3 penalty points.

Achievements.Name: Fish Lover
Achievements.Description: Catch 5 fish of different species during any Tournament mode event or in Free Fishing mode.

Achievements.Name: I Do Attract!
Achievements.Description: Keep a lure's attractiveness level at 90% or higher for more than 30 seconds during a retrieve.

Achievements.Name: Flap Jack
Achievements.Description: Perform the Boat Flipping maneuver 20 times.

Achievements.Name: It's a Monster!
Achievements.Description: Catch a Monster Fish of any species.

Achievements.Name: False Hope
Achievements.Description: Catch 5 fish during any tournament event Weigh In interval of time.

Achievements.Name: Quick Catch
Achievements.Description: Catch a fish of any species in under 1 minute from the start of any event in Tournament mode.

Achievements.Name: Cast Master
Achievements.Description: Cast 500 times.

Achievements.Name: Location Scout
Achievements.Description: Find and cast into 5 different fishing spots in any event in Tournament mode.

Achievements.Name: Top Challenger
Achievements.Description: Complete all the Challenges on any lake in Free Fishing mode.

Achievements.Name: Need a Bigger Boat?
Achievements.Description: Catch 30 fish during any event in Tournament mode or during a single session in Free Fishing mode.

Achievements.Name: The Captain
Achievements.Description: Accumulate 1 hour of boat driving in any game mode.

Achievements.Name: Too Perfect!
Achievements.Description: Accumulate 30 perfect casts in any game mode.

Achievements.Name: Hooking Perfection
Achievements.Description: Accumulate 30 perfect hooks in any game mode.

Achievements.Name: Veteran Angler
Achievements.Description: Complete the Pro Season in Tournament mode.

Achievements.Name: Good Sportsmanship
Achievements.Description: Complete all seasons in Tournament mode with 0 penalty points.

Achievements.Name: Show Off
Achievements.Description: Win any event in Tournament without casting into a fishing spot.

Achievements.Name: Bookworm
Achievements.Description: Enter into all categories in the Fish-O-Pedia.

Achievements.Name: Elite Angler
Achievements.Description: Complete the Legendary Season in Tournament mode.

Achievements.Name: True Legend
Achievements.Description: Catch all 30 Monster Fish.

Achievements.Name: Seeing Spots
Achievements.Description: Cast into at least 60% of all discovered fishing spots across all the lakes in any game mode.

Achievements.Name: Pro Bass Angler
Achievements.Description: Catch at least 50 fish of any of the Bass species in any game mode.

Achievements.Name: Fashionista
Achievements.Description: Unlock every single clothing item for your male or female angler.

Achievements.Name: Weather-Proof
Achievements.Description: Catch a fish in every one of these conditions: morning, noon, evening and sunny, overcast, rainy.

Achievements.Name: Lure Master
Achievements.Description: Catch at least one fish, any fish, with every lure.

Achievements.Name: Like a Sturgeon
Achievements.Description: Finish the Sturgeon Legends event in top 5 using only the 10 lbs. (4.5 Kg) fishing line.

Achievements.Name: Master Challenger
Achievements.Description: Complete all Challenges on all lakes in single player Free Fishing mode.
